attachments.displayName: Serene Stream This week I was in Algonquin Park trying to capture some wildlife and fall colours, but neither was to be seen. I hiked some lookouts and trails to stumble upon nothing but some leaves starting to show their colours. I was happy though when I woke up and got ready, went outside to this view at the river in from of The Mad Musher in Whitney! :D Thanks for viewing and feel free to like, comment or share. object.content:
Serene Stream 

This week I was in Algonquin Park trying to capture some wildlife and fall colours, but neither was to be seen. I hiked some lookouts and trails to stumble upon nothing but some leaves starting to show their colours. I was happy though when I woke up and got ready, went outside to this view at the river in from of The Mad Musher in Whitney! :D Thanks for viewing and feel free to like, comment or share.
